@startuml sequence_service_installation_liba4tv_v3
title Service Installation - broadcast (liba4tv) - v3

' Sabloni: Module 6 Fig.4/6 (tune + table parsing), Module 7 Fig.3/4 (Comedia struktura, scan sequence)
' v3 razlike u odnosu na v2:
'  - ScanControl/ServiceControl/Listeneri su Android-facing wrapper (liba4tv Java API) -> izdvojeni u svoj blok
'  - Comedia Core (MW) + CHAL (TDAL) su odvojen native blok: SAV PAT/PMT/SDT processing ostaje unutra (ne izlazi do TV Inputa)
'  - TV Input samo: pokrene scan preko ScanControl, ceka scanFinished preko ScanListener, zatim cita rezultate preko ServiceControl
'  - Service & Mux DB je nativna baza middleware-a (nezavisna od Androida); TV Input nju ne dodiruje direktno, vec preko ServiceControl

actor User
box "Android app" #EBF5FF
  participant "Live TV App" as App
  participant "Broadcast TvInputService" as TIS
end box

box "liba4tv Java API (Android-facing wrapper)" #E8F5E9
  participant "ComediaRouteManagerControl" as ROUTE
  participant "ScanControl" as SCAN
  participant "ScanListener\n(callback na TIS)" as SCANL
  participant "ServiceControl" as SVC
end box

box "Comedia native middleware" #FFF8E1
  participant "Comedia Core (MW)\nInstall logic + Table parser (PAT/PMT/SDT)\nService & Mux DB (SList+PIDB)" as CORE
  participant "Comedia CHAL (TDAL)\nTDAL_DMD / TDAL_DMX" as CHAL
end box

box "Platform / HAL - demonstration" #FFF3E0
  participant "Tuner SDK / Tuner HAL\n(Cuttlefish: .ts fajl kao izvor)" as TSDK
end box

participant "Android TV Provider\n(TvContract.Channels)" as TVP

User -> App : Initiate scan (first-time install)
App -> TIS : start scan

TIS -> ROUTE : getInstallRoute(RouteManagerMediumType.MEDIUM_IP)
ROUTE --> TIS : routeID
note over ROUTE : MEDIUM_IP = file/URL scan (Cuttlefish);\nMEDIUM_TER bi bio pravi terrestrial scan

TIS -> SCAN : registerListener(scanListener)
TIS -> SCAN : appendList(false)
note right of SCAN : append=false -> obrisi staru listu, kreni od cista
TIS -> SCAN : autoScan(routeID, "file:///data/clear_0002.ts")
SCAN --> TIS : A4TVStatus (poziv prihvacen, scan pokrenut)

== Sve dalje ostaje unutar Comedia native middleware-a ==

SCAN -> CORE : pokreni instalaciju na ruti (routeID)
CORE -> CHAL : TDAL_DMD - otvori izvor (file/tuner) na ruti

CHAL -> TSDK : otvori protokol ('file') + otvori section filtere (PAT/PMT/SDT)
note over TSDK : demonstration-level: file_open / section filter setup\n(ispod: HAL TUNER+DEMUX -> Nexus/Magnum, ref. Module 6 Fig.4/6)
TSDK --> CHAL : izvor zakljucan (locked) + sekcije dostupne

CHAL --> CORE : TDAL_DMX - section data (PAT, PMT, SDT)

group Comedia Core - interna obrada tabela (ne izlazi iz middleware-a)
  CORE -> CORE : parsiraj PAT (PID 0) -> lista servisa + PMT PID-ovi
  CORE -> CORE : parsiraj PMT (po servisu) -> A/V/subtitle PID-ovi, PCR PID, stream type
  CORE -> CORE : parsiraj SDT -> citljiva imena servisa
  CORE -> CORE : upisi/azuriraj Service & Mux DB (SList + PIDB)\n(ONID, TSID, SID, ime, PID-ovi)
  note right of CORE
    Petlja PAT->PMT->SDT se ponavlja za svaki
    pronadjeni servis/multipleks i zavrsava se
    OVDJE, u nativnoj bazi middleware-a.
    TV Input ne dobija sirove tabele,
    vec samo agregovane evente niже.
  end note
end

CORE --> SCAN : interno: progres instalacije (po servisu/multipleksu)
SCAN --> SCANL : tunerLocked(routeId, true)
SCANL --> TIS : tunerLocked(routeId, true)
SCAN --> SCANL : scanProgressChanged(routeId, value)
SCANL --> TIS : scanProgressChanged(routeId, value)
SCAN --> SCANL : installStatus(ScanInstallStatus)
SCANL --> TIS : installStatus(ScanInstallStatus)

note over CORE, CHAL : kada nema vise multipleksa/servisa za obradu na ovoj ruti

CHAL -> TSDK : zatvori section filtere + zatvori izvor (file_close/teardown)
TSDK --> CHAL : interfejs unlocked
CHAL --> CORE : izvor i demux path zatvoreni, route oslobodjen
CORE -> CORE : routeManager - oslobodi install route (routeID)

CORE --> SCAN : instalacija zavrsena (interno)
SCAN --> SCANL : scanFinished(routeId)
SCANL --> TIS : scanFinished(routeId)

== TV Input cita rezultate iz Service & Mux DB preko ServiceControl ==

TIS -> SVC : getServiceListCount(listIndex)
SVC -> CORE : upit nad Service & Mux DB
CORE --> SVC : broj servisa u listi
SVC --> TIS : count

loop za svaki serviceIndex u [0, count)
  TIS -> SVC : getServiceDescriptor(listIndex, serviceIndex)
  SVC -> CORE : upit nad Service & Mux DB
  CORE --> SVC : ServiceDescriptor podaci
  SVC --> TIS : ServiceDescriptor\n(getName, getONID, getTSID, getServiceId, getLCN, isScrambled...)
  TIS -> TVP : insert/update channel (TvContract.Channels)\nmapiranje: ONID/TSID/SID -> Android channel/internal_provider_data
end

TIS -> SCAN : unregisterListener(scanListener)
TIS --> App : Scan complete

@enduml
